data.description: Charming North Oak Cliff Tudor with an open floor plan while maintaining all the character and charm!!! Beautiful large bathroom with double sinks is flanked by the 2 bedrooms. The spacious kitchen features a farm sink with butcher block counters, lots of storage and open shelving, and the utility. If you love outdoor entertaining, this is the backyard for you! Covered large patio, great for enjoying the outdoors and a peaceful waterfall with Koi pond. The dual entrance driveway allows access from both Schooldell & Westmoreland. Welcome HOME!!!
